<SECOND>PM-Wing Cracks,0296</SECOND>
<HEAD>Wing Cracks Send C141 Fleet for Inspection</HEAD>
<DATELINE>ROBINS AIR FORCE BASE, Ga. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
