his articles exposing the My <PERSON> Lai </PERSON> massacre in <LOCATION> Vietnam </LOCATION> when he was a reporter for the <ORGANIZATION> Dispatch </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> News </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Service </ORGANIZATION>. He was also a reporter for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> and for The <ORGANIZATION> New </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> York </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Times </ORGANIZATION>. He left the newspaper to pursue his own writing projects.
