hildren under age 16 were among the 573 Palestinians killed by <LOCATION> Israeli </LOCATION> soldiers or civilians since the uprising against Israeli rule began in December 1987. Forty Israelis also have died. At least 114 Arabs have been killed by fellow Palestinians as suspected collaborators.
