ns were laying out conflicting futures for <PERSON> Hugo </PERSON>, Sheets said. The best advice forecasters could offer, Sheets said, was for coastal residents across the southeastern <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION> to be ready.
