ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> & </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> amp </ORGANIZATION>; Schuster at $ 218.2 million in 1988, according to Educational Marketer. <PERSON> Herb </PERSON> said the proceeds from the sale will be used to reduce part of <ORGANIZATION> Bell </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> & </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> amp </ORGANIZATION>; <PERSON> Howell </PERSON>'s debt of about $ 500 million and to finance internal growth of its remaining businesses, which include republishing databases and a mail handling operation.
